<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 16:08:58 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列国防军预备役军人因在耶路撒冷恐怖袭击中射杀以色列男子而被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/idf-reservist-arrested-for-shooting-israeli-man-during-jerusalem-terror-attack/0000018c-3485-dc03-a9ec-3cffbea00000</link><description>以色列军警宣布逮捕预备役士兵阿维亚德·弗里贾（Aviad Frija），他说他认为被枪杀的犹太男子是袭击耶路撒冷公交车站的巴勒斯坦恐怖分子之一。一位极右翼部长仍称枪手为“民族英雄”</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 15:40:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/idf-reservist-arrested-for-shooting-israeli-man-during-jerusalem-terror-attack/0000018c-3485-dc03-a9ec-3cffbea00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列儿科医生称，哈马斯扣押的儿童遭受“可怕的心理虐待”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/hamas-held-children-hostages-under-terrible-psychological-abuse-pediatrician-says/0000018c-3520-dc03-a9ec-3d7b543a0000</link><description>这位负责照顾从哈马斯囚禁中获释的以色列儿童的医生分享了有关情况的信息，他说：“这些是我从我的祖父那里听到的故事，他是大屠杀的幸存者。”</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 15:28:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/hamas-held-children-hostages-under-terrible-psychological-abuse-pediatrician-says/0000018c-3520-dc03-a9ec-3d7b543a0000</guid></item><item><title>考虑到他们的利益，一些中东大国并不急于送行哈马斯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/their-interests-in-mind-some-regional-powers-arent-rushing-to-see-off-hamas/0000018c-3434-d5f2-a5cc-7634c3d50000</link><description>尽管面临美国和以色列的压力，土耳其埃尔多安、埃及塞西和其他领导人仍然认为，即使在战后，该恐怖组织仍可能是巴勒斯坦领导层的一部分</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 15:04:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/their-interests-in-mind-some-regional-powers-arent-rushing-to-see-off-hamas/0000018c-3434-d5f2-a5cc-7634c3d50000</guid></item><item><title>犹太人什么时候开始在光明节点燃蜡烛？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-12-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/when-did-jews-start-lighting-candles-on-hanukkah/0000017f-db2c-d3ff-a7ff-fbacdaba0000</link><description>现代传统认为光明节蜡烛是随着节日而诞生的，但约瑟夫斯没有听说过它们：看来我们是从异教徒农神节借来的</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 14:20:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-12-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/when-did-jews-start-lighting-candles-on-hanukkah/0000017f-db2c-d3ff-a7ff-fbacdaba0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯犯下了有记录的暴行。但一些虚假故事却让否认者大吃一惊</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/hamas-committed-documented-atrocities-but-a-few-false-stories-feed-the-deniers/0000018c-34f3-da74-afce-b5fbe24f0000</link><description>哈马斯恐怖分子 10 月 7 日犯下反人类罪的大量证据不应被以色列搜救组织、军官甚至萨拉·内塔尼亚胡散布的未经证实的故事所污染。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 14:18:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/hamas-committed-documented-atrocities-but-a-few-false-stories-feed-the-deniers/0000018c-34f3-da74-afce-b5fbe24f0000</guid></item><item><title>法院审理阻止荷兰向以色列出口 F-35 零部件的诉讼</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/court-hears-suit-to-stop-netherlands-exporting-f-35-parts-to-israel/0000018c-34e9-d340-a3cc-f7ffe2cd0000</link><description>荷兰人权组织辩称，以色列在加沙袭击中使用了美国制造的飞机，造成平民死亡</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 13:10:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/court-hears-suit-to-stop-netherlands-exporting-f-35-parts-to-israel/0000018c-34e9-d340-a3cc-f7ffe2cd0000</guid></item><item><title>在加沙去世之前，他创作了这部史诗般的犹太卷轴</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2023-12-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/before-dying-in-gaza-he-created-this-epic-jewish-scroll/0000018c-34a5-d0a6-a19f-bfa7bb900000</link><description>21 岁的埃坦·罗森茨威格 (Eitan Rosenzweig) 在加沙被杀。他的艺术作品在他身后流传至今：“这个人将会变得很特别，”已故吉瓦蒂士兵的策展人波拉特·所罗门 (Porat Salomon) 说道。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 12:49:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2023-12-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/before-dying-in-gaza-he-created-this-epic-jewish-scroll/0000018c-34a5-d0a6-a19f-bfa7bb900000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日大屠杀之前，哈马斯做空以色列股票是否赚了数百万美元？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/did-hamas-make-billions-betting-against-israeli-shares-before-october-7-massacre/0000018c-348d-d5f2-a5cc-769d7bea0000</link><description>在哈马斯袭击前几天，特拉维夫和华尔街市场上针对以色列的豪赌赚了数十亿美元。似乎有人提前知道了这个计划</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 12:34:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/did-hamas-make-billions-betting-against-israeli-shares-before-october-7-massacre/0000018c-348d-d5f2-a5cc-769d7bea0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对英国和法国等一些欧洲国家发出旅行警告</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-issues-travel-warning-for-some-european-countries-including-u-k-and-france/0000018c-349f-d5f2-a5cc-769f24b10000</link><description>国家安全委员会呼吁海外以色列公民“避免展示以色列和犹太人的标志并避免聚会”</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 12:11:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-issues-travel-warning-for-some-european-countries-including-u-k-and-france/0000018c-349f-d5f2-a5cc-769f24b10000</guid></item><item><title>加沙失职：联合国秘书长古特雷斯必须下台</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-04/ty-article-opinion/.premium/dereliction-of-duty-on-gaza-un-secretary-general-guterres-must-go/0000018c-33f2-dc03-a9ec-3ffb78620000</link><description>安东尼奥·古特雷斯在哈马斯 10 月 7 日袭击以色列后发表的评论表明，他的态度充耳不闻，不仅因为这次袭击引发了地区性、甚至可能是全球性的安全危机，而且还因为他的消极态度。这是联合国在世界舞台上的责任</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 12:06:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-04/ty-article-opinion/.premium/dereliction-of-duty-on-gaza-un-secretary-general-guterres-must-go/0000018c-33f2-dc03-a9ec-3ffb78620000</guid></item><item><title>以色列女演员盖尔·加朵呼吁对哈马斯性暴力保持沉默</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-actress-gal-gadot-calls-out-silence-over-sexual-based-violence-by-hamas/0000018c-347f-d5f2-a5cc-767fe34b0000</link><description>这位《神奇女侠》明星写道：“世界辜负了 10 月 7 日的女性，这是一个需要果断回应的紧急情况。”她与其他以色列和犹太女性一起强调了国际社会在谴责哈马斯暴行方面的犹豫不决</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 11:36:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-actress-gal-gadot-calls-out-silence-over-sexual-based-violence-by-hamas/0000018c-347f-d5f2-a5cc-767fe34b0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙朋友的个人恳求</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/a-personal-plea-from-a-friend-in-gaza/0000018c-3480-dc03-a9ec-3cfbc1670000</link><description>“我们真正需要的是推土机来挖掘并将我们深深地埋入我们的土地”</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 11:14:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/a-personal-plea-from-a-friend-in-gaza/0000018c-3480-dc03-a9ec-3cfbc1670000</guid></item><item><title>弗吉尼亚州光明节烛光仪式因以色列和加沙紧张局势而取消</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/hanukkah-candle-lighting-ceremony-in-virginia-cancelled-over-israel-gaza-tensions/0000018c-33d9-dc03-a9ec-3ffba2f20000</link><description>据弗吉尼亚半岛犹太联合社区称，活动组织者只有在加沙停火的呼吁下才同意恢复仪式。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 10:50:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/hanukkah-candle-lighting-ceremony-in-virginia-cancelled-over-israel-gaza-tensions/0000018c-33d9-dc03-a9ec-3ffba2f20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列如何确定远方哈马斯扣押的人质的死亡？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/how-did-israel-determine-hamas-killed-hostages-left-in-gaza/0000018c-342a-dc03-a9ec-3c7bbf050000</link><description>为确定人质命运而建立的复杂而雄心勃勃的项目：一个新委员会正在观察、分析和比较视频剪辑，并使用支持证据和情报信息，以得出关键结论</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 10:40:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/how-did-israel-determine-hamas-killed-hostages-left-in-gaza/0000018c-342a-dc03-a9ec-3c7bbf050000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人质乔纳森·萨梅拉诺的家人得知他的死讯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/family-of-israeli-hostage-jonathan-samerano-informed-of-his-death/0000018c-3406-d5f2-a5cc-761679a50000</link><description>这名 21 岁的男子从 Nova 音乐节逃往 Be&amp;#39;eri，随后在那里遭到枪杀和绑架</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 09:52:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/family-of-israeli-hostage-jonathan-samerano-informed-of-his-death/0000018c-3406-d5f2-a5cc-761679a50000</guid></item><item><title>本·格维尔任命的人员在枪支许可证上偷工减料后，枪支许可部门负责人辞职</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/top-firearms-official-resigns-after-ben-gvirs-appointees-cut-corners-on-gun-permits/0000018c-33cb-da74-afce-b7fb542b0000</link><description>本格维尔国家安全部枪支许可负责人伊斯雷尔·阿维萨尔 (Yisrael Avisar) 在议会听证会上表示，官员向没有接受过适当培训的人发放武器许可证</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 08:42:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/top-firearms-official-resigns-after-ben-gvirs-appointees-cut-corners-on-gun-permits/0000018c-33cb-da74-afce-b7fb542b0000</guid></item><item><title>三名以色列士兵在加沙地面行动中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/three-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-ground-operation/0000018c-338c-d0a6-a19f-bfae2e330000</link><description>军方公布了周日另外三名阵亡士兵的姓名 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，已有 401 名以色列士兵阵亡</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 07:11:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/three-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-ground-operation/0000018c-338c-d0a6-a19f-bfae2e330000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军袭击黎巴嫩真主党目标时向以色列中部发射火箭弹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article-live/idf-chief-vows-to-fight-as-hard-in-the-south-as-we-did-in-the-north/0000018c-32c7-dc03-a9ec-3eff0d8c0000</link><description>以色列国防军周日公布了在加沙战斗中丧生的三名士兵的姓名 ■ 被认为在加沙被绑架的 21 岁以色列人被宣布死亡 ■ 以色列军队表示，自加沙地面行动开始以来已找到 800 个哈马斯隧道竖井 ■ 美国官员称没有进行正式谈判关于人质释放 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列至少有 1,200 名平民和士兵被杀；加沙仍有超过 159 名人质被扣押 ■ 哈马斯卫生部：加沙至少有 15,500 人死亡</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 04:11:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article-live/idf-chief-vows-to-fight-as-hard-in-the-south-as-we-did-in-the-north/0000018c-32c7-dc03-a9ec-3eff0d8c0000</guid></item><item><title>尽量减少加沙平民的死亡符合以色列的最佳利益</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-12-04/ty-article-opinion/minimizing-deaths-of-gazan-civilians-is-in-israels-best-interest/0000018c-3165-dc03-a9ec-3d7f8f000000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 01:57:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-12-04/ty-article-opinion/minimizing-deaths-of-gazan-civilians-is-in-israels-best-interest/0000018c-3165-dc03-a9ec-3d7f8f000000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡审判恢复；利库德集团称其为“耻辱”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-trial-to-resume-likud-mk-calls-it-a-disgrace/0000018c-3169-da74-afce-b5f9cfce0000</link><description>针对总理的案件因加沙战争中断两个月后将重新启动。据称，内塔尼亚胡采取了有利于贝泽克电信的监管措施，以换取瓦拉网站（原归贝泽克电信所有）的有利媒体报道</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 00:53:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-04/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-trial-to-resume-likud-mk-calls-it-a-disgrace/0000018c-3169-da74-afce-b5f9cfce0000</guid></item></channel></rss>